text: Emilné Rácz was a female Hungarian international table tennis player. ==Table tennis career== She won a silver medal at the 1933 World Table Tennis Championships in the women's doubles with Magda Gál. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:Hungarian female table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Emilné Rácz
